[Game introduction]
"The Three Kingdoms - Strategy" is a military game masterpiece officially authorized by KOEI TECMO to be released in Vietnam!
Entering this 3D ancient battlefield, you will transform into a King during the chaotic Three Kingdoms period.
Start growing your power from scratch, recruit famous generals, and order your army to march;
